Module org.apache.jena.arq
Package org.apache.jena.sparql.exec

Interface QueryExecMod

All Known Subinterfaces:
QueryExecBuilder
All Known Implementing Classes:
QueryExecBuilderAdapter, QueryExecDatasetBuilder, QueryExecHTTPBuilder
public interface QueryExecMod
Aspects of a building a QueryExec that can be changed before use. This is more limited than QueryExecBuilder and assumes that the query and target for the query have been setup.
